        <hr/>
                        
<div class="txt-block" id="name-bio-text">
        <div class="name-trivia-bio-text">
                      <div class="inline" itemprop="description">
Ramin Niami is a producer and editor, known for <a href="/title/tt0313459?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk1">Paris</a> (2003), <a href="/title/tt2040504?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk2">Shirin in Love</a> (2014) and <a href="/title/tt0120162?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk3">Somewhere in the City</a> (1998). He is married to <a href="/name/nm0733470?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk4">Karen Robson</a>.            <span class="see-more inline nobr-only">
                    <a href="/name/nm0629191/bio?ref_=nm_ov_bio_sm"
>See full bio</a> &raquo;
            </span>
</div>        </div>
</div>

                        

                        
                        
                   </td>
